   The Massachusetts governor's commercial was a similar blend of
speech-making and images from the campaign trail and bosom of his
family.
   It showed him fielding questions on issues that have plagued him
all campaign long, including his record on crime, the environment
and his relunctance to respond to the negative attacks.
   He said in reply that he had a record of achievement on crime and
